<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Student Application</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T"
        crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body>
    <form>
        <h1>Student Application Form</h1>
        <p>
            Base Camp Coding Academy
            <br>
            301 North Main Street
            <br>
            Water Valley, MS 38965
            <br>
            http://www.basecampcodingacademy.org
            <br>
            <br>
            Thank you for applying to BCCA! This is the first step of a two part application process. Strong candidates
            will be contacted for an in-person interview, so make sure to check your email for follow-up! Base Camp is
            a targeted program for north Mississippi high school seniors able to live within driving distance of Water
            Valley.
            <br>
            <br>
            Space at BCCA is very limited. This is a huge opportunity, and responsibility. Please help us understand
            why you are the right person to receive this opportunity. In order to be eligible to apply you must have
            first been nominated by a teacher, employer, or other qualified individual who can speak to your abilities.
        </p>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="studentNameInput">Name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="studentNameInput" placeholder="Enter name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="studentAgeInput">Age</label>
            <input type="number" class="form-control" id="studentAgeInput" placeholder="Enter Age">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="studentPhoneNumberInput">Phone Number</label>
            <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="studentPhoneNumberInput" placeholder="123-123-1234">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group" class="form-group">
            <label for="studentEmailInput">Email address</label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="studentEmailInput" placeholder="Enter email">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="studentSchoolInput">School you currently attend</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="studentSchoolInput">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="">Expected Graduation Date:</label>
            <input type="date" class="form-control" id="">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>How did you hear about BCCA?</label>
            <input type="text">
        </div>
        <div class="form-check">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="radio1" name="radioButton" value="option" checked>
            <label class="form-check-label" for="radio1">Yes</label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-check">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="radio2" name="radioButton" value="option">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="radio2">No</label>
        </div>
        <div>
            <label for="">Current Plans for Next Year:</label>
            <input type="text">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <p>Base Camp Coding Academy is looking for students with the aptitude, and the dedication, to succeed in this
            program. Please share stories and examples of these two traits that demonstrate why you believe you will
            make an excellent candidate</p>
        <hr>
        <p>For example, you might include times when you were able to think logically or creatively to solve a problem,
            or when you overcame a challenging situation with school, work, or a project.
            <hr>
        </p>
        <div>
            <label for="">Aptitude:</label>
            <p class="text-muted">Please share a specific example of when you were a strong problem solver.</p>
            <input type="text">
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <label for="">Dedication/Work Ethic:</label>
            <p class="text-muted">Please share a specific example of your dedication and work ethic.</p>
            <input type="text">
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <label for="">Passion/Persistence:</label>
            <p class="text-muted">Please tell us about something you are passionate about and have worked hard to
                achieve. This can be clubs, sports teams, hobbies, church groups, etc.</p>
            <input type="text">
        </div>
        <p>Base Camp Coding Academy admits students of any race, color, national and ethnic origin to all the rights,
            privileges, programs, and activities generally accorded or made available to students at the school. It
            does not discriminate on the basis of race, color, national and ethnic origin in administration of its
            educational policies, admissions policies, scholarship and loan programs, and athletic and other
            school-administered programs.</p>
        <button>Submit</button>
    </form>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>